            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Nymphis <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> Iul<lb break="no" n="2"/>ius C<supplied reason="lost">r</supplied>esc<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied><expan><abbr>ns</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXII <expan><abbr>Pr</abbr><ex>imigeniae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>omitianae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1 u. 2 befinden sich auf einer tabula ansata an der Vorderseite der corona; Z. 3-4 auf dem Mittelteil, darüber ein schwer deutbares Relief, darunter wohl eine gelagerte Nymphe; Z. 5 auf der crepido. Lesungs- und Ergänzungsvorschlag nach Matijević. (B): CIL 13, 07724; Lehner: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
